readme:
# Proton Monokai

A monokai syntax theme for Atom to work with [Proton UI](https://atom.io/packages/proton).

Originally converted from [kevinsawicki](https://github.com/kevinsawicki)'s Monokai [port](https://github.com/kevinsawicki/monokai). Changed the [Proton Monokai](https://github.com/jdsimcoe/proton-kai) Version from [jdsimcoe](https://github.com/jdsimcoe) to fit the [One Dark UI Theme](https://atom.io/themes/one-dark-ui).

![Screenshot](http://cl.ly/image/2Y3v0S0V3Y04/Image%202014-05-14%20at%207.59.58%20AM.png)
